descript.purpose:
This dataset can contribute towards creating an extensive database of soil properties of the intensive study sites (Areas A, B, C) of NGEE-Arctic; the detailed metadata will also be valuable to all studies based in the Arctic that have soil as an integral component; e.g. Soil Biogeochemistry, Microbiology, Hydrology to list a few.&#xD;
&#xD;
BGC1.3       Representative soil property data for subsurface modules
